        <Parent_String>scale (relative size) [300056307], form and composition concepts [300056242], formal concepts (artistic concept) [300164603], artistic concepts [300168394], concepts in the arts and humanities [300056107], Associated Concepts (hierarchy name) [300055126], Associated Concepts Facet [300264086]</Parent_String>
